When building this from scratch you will need the
following packages:

    inkscape
    ttf-droid
    ttf-dejavu 
    ttf-sazanami-gothic
    texlive-fonts-recommended
    texlive-extra-utils
    texlive-xetex
    texlive-latex-extra
    texlive-latex-recommended
    latex-cjk-xcjk
    git-core
    make

After that, you will hopefully only to give 'make'
